tle_of_the_Silarus" title="Battle of the Silarus">Silarus</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Herdonia_(212_BC)" title="Battle of Herdonia (212 BC)">1st&#160;Herdonia</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_the_Upper_Baetis" title="Battle of the Upper Baetis">Upper&#160;Baetis</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Capua_(211_BC)" title="Battle of Capua (211 BC)">2nd&#160;Capua</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Herdonia_(210_BC)" title="Battle of Herdonia (210 BC)">2nd&#160;Herdonia</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Numistro" title="Battle of Numistro">Numistro</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Canusium" title="Battle of Canusium">Asculum</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Tarentum_(209_BC)" title="Battle of Tarentum (209 BC)">2nd Tarentum</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Cartagena_(209_BC)" title="Battle of Cartagena (209 BC)">New Carthage</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Baecula" title="Battle of Baecula">Baecula</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Grumentum" title="Battle of Grumentum">Grumentum</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_the_Metaurus" title="Battle of the Metaurus">Metaurus</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Ilipa" title="Battle of Ilipa">Ilipa</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Crotona" title="Battle of Crotona">Crotona</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Utica_(203_BC)" title="Battle of Utica (203 BC)">Utica</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_the_Great_Plains" title="Battle of the Great Plains">Great&#160;Plains</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Cirta" title="Battle of Cirta">Cirta</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Po_Valley_Raid" title="Po Valley Raid">Po&#160;Valley</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Zama" title="Battle of Zama">Zama</a></div>
